<typeStatus id="182E8838FFB6FFC8C4F502389432FB80" box="[237,281,1098,1122]" pageId="1" pageNumber="390">type</typeStatus>
species kept at the Zoological Museum, Copenhagen, http://www.daim.snm.ku.dk/The-digitized-type-collection). 
